Probably, Ukrainian equivalent of Monty Python's Flying Circus :)

This comedy show aired on Ukrainian and Russian TV in 1996-1999.

It was filmed in Kyiv at Dovzhenko Film Studios.

Spoken languages: Ukrainian, Russian and mixture of them called "Surzhyk".



Quality: TVRip [TV->VHS->Digital video]

Container: AVI

Video: XVID 640x480 25 fps ~800 Kbps

Audio: MPEG Audio Layer 3 44.1 kHz mono 96 Kbps



Collection of 44 episodes (chronologically unsorted).



This show is hard to find now 'cause of no official releases on DVD.
